title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
OB: In the Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the report parameters are not displayed.
EB: In the Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the report parameters should be displayed.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Create multiple report parameters. 2. Set default values for each parameter. 3. Drag the parameters to the Layout section. Open the Show Report Parameters' dialog to verify that the default values are not shown.
